<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>hapax — credits</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://ryanklee.github.io/hapax-assets/css/hapax-core.css">
  <style>
    body { font-family: "Px437 IBM VGA 8x16", "PxPlus IBM VGA 8x16", monospace; }
    table.credits-table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; }
    table.credits-table th, table.credits-table td { padding: 0.4em 0.8em; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }
    table.credits-table thead tr { border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor; }
    table.credits-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) { opacity: 0.85; }
    code { white-space: nowrap; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="e-window" data-title="credits">
  <div class="body">
    <p>Every authentic asset incorporated into Hapax.
       In the hip-hop production tradition: these are the samples.</p>

    <table class="credits-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>asset</th>
          <th>origin</th>
          <th>author</th>
          <th>license</th>
          <th>extracted</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {%- for asset in model.assets %}
        <tr>
          <td><code>{{ asset.source }}/{{ asset.kind }}/{{ asset.name }}</code></td>
          <td>{{ asset.path }}</td>
          <td><a href="{{ asset.source_url }}" rel="noopener">{{ asset.author }}</a></td>
          <td>{{ asset.license }}</td>
          <td>{{ asset.extracted_date }}</td>
        </tr>
        {%- endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="e-window" data-title="license obligations">
  <div class="body">
    <p>Licenses present in this library:</p>
    <ul>
      {%- for license_id in model.licenses_present %}
      <li><strong>{{ license_id }}</strong></li>
      {%- endfor %}
    </ul>

    <p>Per-asset attribution lines (verbatim from upstream):</p>
    <ul>
      {%- for asset in model.assets %}
      <li>{{ asset.attribution_line }}</li>
      {%- endfor %}
    </ul>

    <p>CC-BY-SA-4.0 ShareAlike: derivative works of any CC-BY-SA-4.0
       asset above inherit the same license. Hapax does not modify the
       upstream bytes of CC-BY-SA-4.0 assets (format-only transcodes
       like TTF→WOFF2 are not derivatives).</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="e-window" data-title="meta">
  <div class="body">
    <p>This page is auto-generated from the aesthetic library's
       <code>_manifest.yaml</code> + per-source
       <code>provenance.yaml</code>. Any new asset added to the
       library appears here automatically on the next publish cycle.</p>
    <p>Source of truth:
       <a href="https://github.com/ryanklee/hapax-council/blob/main/assets/aesthetic-library/_manifest.yaml"
          rel="noopener">hapax-council/assets/aesthetic-library/</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
